text: Rawhead Rex is a 1986 British Irish horror movie directed by George Pavlou and starring David Dukes, Kelly Piper, Niall Toibin, Niall O'Brien, Hugh O'Connor, Donal McCann. It was distributed by Empire Pictures. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1986 horror movies Category:British horror movies Category:Irish horror movies
